data.description:
SELLER IS OFFERING 10K!!! Use as rate buydown or towards closing cost.

Welcome to the beautiful area of Legacy West. With easy access to DNT and 121 everything you need  is well within reach. Granite Park Boardwalk is just a brief 3 minute walk as well as Shops at Legacy. Fine dining and luxury shopping compliments this sleek 3 story townhouse. First floor has an inviting living space with built-in surround sound that ushers you to the second floor. Another living space awaits you just passed the open kitchen with built-in wine cooler just inside the considerably sized island. Third floor hosts all bedrooms and laundry. Owners suite consists of 2 walk in closets, double sinks, jacuzzi tub, separate shower with 4 body jets and a Juliet balcony.  Garage offers appx 200 square feet of space for additional storage. Buyer to do their due diligence on schools, taxes, HOA's, POA's etc.
